Summarise an 'mreg' object

summary.mreg.Rd

This function serves as a summary method for class 'mreg'. It computes summary statistics and results for a fitted linear model.

# S3 method for mreg
summary(x)

Arguments

x

an object of class 'mreg', presumably an output from the mreg() function.

Value

a list containing summary statistics and results

Details

Examples

mtcars$am <- factor(mtcars$am)
fit <- mreg(mpg ~ ., mtcars)
summary(fit)
